cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CE 

The paper discusses the firefly algorithm, which is a type of Swarm Intelligence used for optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper discusses the application of the algorithm in various areas, indicating that it could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The algorithm is also used in engineering practice, which suggests it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
